## Limitations

The findings in this report are based on a limited selection of sources and may not encompass all perspectives on the topic. Additionally, the success of social movements can be context-dependent, varying significantly across different cultural, political, and social environments. Further research could provide a more comprehensive understanding of the factors influencing the success of social movements.